subTitle: Baalveer goes to Kaal Lok and fights Timnasa. He is weak, but he has the blessings of two mothers with him. He eventually manages to trick Timnasa and defeat her. Then Baalveer takes Vivaan, who is unconscious.

title: Champions Ka Tashan
subTitle: The host, judges and the contestants invite Santa Claus on the occasion of Christmas. Later, the contestants stage an act together.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: An old man robs Jethalal of his lucky bangle while he has tea with Popatlal. Shocked, Jethalal goes to the store to tell Bagha and Nattu Kaka about this.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Manhar Manmoji walks to Jethalal's shop and claims that it is his. He even sells a product to a customer, much to Nattu Kaka and Bagha's confusion.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Jethalal complains to Inspector Pandey about Manhar invading his shop; Rajkumar Singhania visits Jethalal's store but gets forced to leave by Manhar Manmoji.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Jethalal brings Manhar Manmoji to Gokuldham Society by force. During the ordeal, Manmoji gets forced to travel with Bhide on his scooter.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Daya meets Manhar Manmoji and tells her father-in-law that he has gone mad; a team of news reporters barge into Gokuldham to talk to Manmoji.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Samir meets his father, Manhar Manmoji, in Gokuldham Society. After reuniting, Manmoji tells him that he will permanently stay in Jethalal's home.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Taarak convinces Popatlal to call Asit and ask him to arrange a marriage for him. However, Asit refuses to meet Popatlal when he comes to his office.

title: India's Got Talent
subTitle: India's Got Talent is back with phenomenal acts by the participants that will salute and honour the talent of India along with Badshah, Kirron Kher and Shilpa Shetty.

title: Super Dancer -- Chapter 4
subTitle: Various skilled children from around the country present captivating dance performances as they vie for the esteemed title.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Anjali and Taarak discuss the idea of Popatlal's marriage. Meanwhile, the Gokuldham Society kids tell Champaklal about their new game.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Madhavi gets into a misunderstanding with Bhide about her cooking. Later, all the men get together at Abdul's soda shop.

title: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
subTitle: Jethalal's thoughtless remark about marriage makes Popatlal angry. Later, a mysterious stranger begins playing the violin at Gokuldham Society.
